{"tid":242418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與許亦妮　何佩瑜傳緋聞","createTime":"2017-05-14T01:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T01:32:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be6d2ce60b05b50ac639c1f1f5f853bbab73b678","tid":242418,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20020887&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20020887%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c77ba749\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20020887%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&h=3566b83f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20020887&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514</a><br />\n<br />\n與許亦妮　何佩瑜傳緋聞<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在北角街頭遇襲的盧啟邦來頭不小，剛於2個月前才獲上巿公司太陽世紀集團董事會委任為執行董事，進入集團權力核心。<br />\n現年37歲的盧啟邦被視為青年才俊，曾經擔任CEC Telecom的資深副總經理，其後曾加入上巿公司嘉年華國際出任執行董事，現為太陽世紀集團執董。<br />\n事業得意的盧啟邦感情生活亦多姿多采，由於其所屬集團的子公司太陽娛樂文化曾經投資多部電影，令盧啟邦因而有不少機會與女星交往，緋聞女友一個接一個，當中包括港姐出身的許亦妮，其後又傳戀上有份參演電影《喜愛夜蒲3》的何佩瑜（Jeana）及文凱玲（Connie），之後又搭上𡃁模Hera等。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n盧啟邦2013年被拍到接送緋聞女友許亦妮。<br />\n<br />\n電動房車賽冠軍<br />\n<br />\n此外，盧啟邦亦愛好名車，曾經擁有一部價值469萬元的法拉利458 Spider開篷跑車、兩部麥拿倫MP4跑車及寶馬M5等，去年參與中環首屆電動房車挑戰賽，力壓方中信、錢嘉樂、郭富城奪得第一位。<br />\n■記者莫家文<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n洗米華愛將遭伏擊　司機護主捱斬<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;3小時前"},{"pid":"a0da348ae42d21289efe7b0258e9acf3ba247323","tid":242418,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"盧啟邦2013年被拍到接送緋聞女友許亦妮。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170514/large/14la3p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F14la3p7.jpg&h=a6c71c6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2444f4c1ebed3afce3d2eec30cc129a01dc1fbf","tid":242418,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:32:32.000Z","msg":"包養咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}